Description: Access public spatial data from the Spanish Cadastre through
    its 'INSPIRE' and related web services. Retrieve cadastral parcel,
    building, address and georeferenced map image data and convert between
    cadastral references and coordinates.
License: GPL-2
URL: https://ropenspain.github.io/CatastRo/,
    https://github.com/rOpenSpain/CatastRo
